doc:
Returns a slice of all values in the underlying vector, in arbitrary
order.

# Examples

Basic usage:

```
use std::collections::BinaryHeap;
use std::io::{self, Write};

let heap = BinaryHeap::from([1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]);

io::sink().write(heap.as_slice()).unwrap();
```
